name: Raymond Diaz
summary:
Raymond Diaz is a 34-year-old, 5'10", Hispanic/Latino man, who identifies as gay and uses he/him/his pronouns. He is an Emergency Room Nurse working in the healthcare industry in Los Angeles, California but originally hails from San Diego. Fluent in English, Spanish, and French, he values family, career, and adventure. He enjoys traveling, photography, cooking, and fitness.

Raymond is a Catholic and holds liberal political views. He is looking for a life partner and is interested in a monogamous relationship. Although he doesn't currently have children, he intends to in the future. He enjoys the company of his dog and exercises actively. He occasionally drinks but doesn't smoke or use marijuana or any drugs.

He seeks a partner who is between 28-40 years old, with a height range of 5'5" to 6'2", who doesn't currently have children but wants to in the future. He prefers someone who is also active, occasionally drinks, and does not smoke or use drugs.
